  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个混合云架构图，核心是在Cloud Environment里部署两套App Server做负载均衡，外面通过Corporate Network让管理员接入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cloud Environment",
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2",
        "Corporate Network"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，负载均衡器放在Cloud Environment里面对吧？那管理员从公司内网进来，是先经过防火墙还是直接连VPN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer",
        "Firewall",
        "VPN Connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "管理员走Admin Portal，先过Firewall，然后Admin Portal再连VPN，最后VPN隧道接到Load Balancer。这样内外网隔离比较安全。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Firewall",
        "AdminPortal",
        "VPN Connection",
        "Load Balancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Corporate Network子图画出来：Firewall连到Admin Portal，Admin Portal再连VPN Connection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Firewall",
        "AdminPortal",
        "VPN Connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Cloud Environment这边，Load Balancer下游挂两台App Server，然后两台服务器共享同一个Redis Cache和Database Cluster，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load Balancer",
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2",
        "Cache",
        "Database Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Cache和DB都要双连，保证两台App Server都能访问。不过Internet入口你打算怎么画？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2",
        "Cache",
        "Database Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Internet我画在子图外面，作为外部流量入口。一条线连到Firewall给管理后台用，另一条直接连Load Balancer给普通用户访问。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "Firewall",
        "Load Balancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样公网用户和管理员走不同路径。VPN那条线记得要从Corporate Network穿出来连到LB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VPN Connection",
        "Load Balancer",
        "Corporate Network"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，VPN Connection指向Load Balancer。我检查一下：Internet有两条出边，一条到Firewall，一条到LB；VPN到LB；LB分叉到两台App Server。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "Firewall",
        "Load Balancer",
        "VPN Connection",
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，App Server和Cache之间的连线，你画的是单向还是双向？其实只需要从App Server指向Cache就行，表示调用关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2",
        "Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前是单向的，AppServer1和AppServer2都指向Cache。Database Cluster也是同样的画法，两台服务器各自连到DB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AppServer1",
        "AppServer2",
        "Cache",
        "Database Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没问题。不过Corporate Network里的节点命名，Admin Portal中间要不要加空格？还有VPN Connection写全称会不会太长？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AdminPortal",
        "VPN Connection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持AdminPortal连在一起吧，跟AppServer1的命名风格统一。VPN Connection用全称，这样跟Internet、Firewall这些并列的时候语义更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AdminPortal",
        "VPN Connection",
        "AppServer1",
        "Internet",
        "Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同意。最后确认一下Database Cluster的图标，用圆柱形表示数据库对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "是的，DB用了圆柱括号[()]的样式。Internet用了双圆括号表示外部网络。整体结构：两个子图Cloud Environment和Corporate Network，加上外部Internet节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database Cluster",
        "Internet",
        "Cloud Environment",
        "Corporate Network"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个架构图可以用了。负载均衡、双活服务器、共享缓存和数据库，加上安全的VPN管理通道，所有关键要素都齐了。",
